snippet.title: Johhny Depp and Amber Heard? Its YES or NO?
snippet.description:
So Johhny Depp and Amber Heard have been married for 15 months.

The Facts: They met on the set of Rum Diary February 3,2015. She's 30 and he's 52. Johnny Depps mother of 81 years just passed away after an illness. May she rest in peace. Amber is seeking $50,000 a month ( that is someone's yearly salary, yes I typed that) for spousal support. 

 Its YES or NO QUESTIONS? 
1. Is Amber just seeking money or a gold digger?
2. Is Johnny Depp abusive?
3. Did the cops side with Johnny?

So weigh in we wanna hear your thoughts?
